DESCRIPTION:Join GRAMMY-nominated singer-songwriter Anne Wilson for the se
 cond leg of The STARS Tour\, this Spring. Come get a first look at new mus
 ic from her recently released album STARS\, alongside fan favorites like '
 Rain in the Rearview\,' 'Strong\,' 'Hey Girl\,' and her multi-week No. 1 s
 mash 'My Jesus.' Don't miss a powerful night of music\, worship\, and a lo
 ok at what's to come.
LOCATION:Indiana University - Bloomington
URL:https://limestonepost.org/calendar/#/details/the-stars-tour-featuring-
 anne-wilson/17495001/2026-04-09T19
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
