BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Comedian Jeff Allen
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260409T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260409T210000
UID:260405NZns1EvFvEy46xaO6-ZCgQ
DESCRIPTION:Jeff Allen may \\(or may not\\) want to admit it\, but he’s 
 getting old. At 69\, Jeff is staring down his 70th year and decided it mig
 ht be time to think about slowing down. The result? My First Final Farewel
 l Tour kicks off March 1\, 2026. Yes\, you read that right—“First” a
 nd “Final” in the same sentence—because Jeff’s not totally sure he
 ’s done. \\(After all\, Cher had 20 farewell tours\, and Elton John is s
 till out there.\\)\n\nBrought to you by Mad Hatter Shows & Tivoli Theatre
LOCATION:Historic Tivoli Theatre
URL:https://www.spencertivoli.org/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
