BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:African American Dance Company Spring Concert
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260418T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260418T213000
UID:260218Jg0O45si70OmhebPZ_zTDw
DESCRIPTION:The legendary **African American Dance Company** presents it
 s Annual Spring Concert on Saturday\, April 18\, 2026\, 7:30 p.m. at Buski
 rk-Chumley Theater in Bloomington\, IN.\n\nDirected by Baba Stafford C. Be
 rry Jr.\, the African American Dance Company shares movement traditions fr
 om Africa\, the diaspora\, and from African American culture. Since its fo
 unding in 1974\, the African American Dance Company has performed througho
 ut Indiana\, in New York City\, and internationally in China\, Jamaica\, a
 nd Cuba. The company’s repertoire includes African dance styles\, contem
 porary\, modern\, jazz\, hip-hop\, and various cultural forms.\n\nThe Afri
 can American Dance Company is a course offered for credit through the Depa
 rtment of African American and African Diaspora Studies\, and is one of th
 ree performing ensembles managed by African American Arts Institute at Ind
 iana University Bloomington.
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/african-american-dance-company-sprin
 g-concert-april-18-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
