BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:ABRA Cadabra
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260419T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260419T214500
UID:2602114L8OeLEO3kapTawq8T0_aQ
DESCRIPTION:**Attention all ABBA fans!** Get ready for a night of glitter
 ing costumes\, irresistible melodies\, and pure joy when ABRA Cadabra – 
 the internationally acclaimed ABBA tribute band – takes the stage at Bur
 kirk-Chumley Theater in Bloomington on April 19\, 2026 @ 7:30pm.\n\nFor 25
  years\, ABRA Cadabra has been captivating audiences across the globe with
  faithful yet fresh performances of ABBA’s timeless hits. From “Dancin
 g Queen” to “Mamma Mia” and “Take a Chance on Me\,” the band ble
 nds meticulous musical detail with colorful visuals and an atmosphere desi
 gned to get audiences on their feet.\n\nThe result is a high-energy\, fami
 ly-friendly spectacle featuring a live band\, dancers\, dazzling costumes\
 , and multiple wardrobe changes. Audiences are encouraged to sing\, clap\,
  and dance along\, creating a shared moment of nostalgia and celebration.\
 n\nConnect with ABRA Cadabra on Facebook & Instagram @ATributeToABBA and o
 nline at www.iloveabba.com\n\nHere’s what our fans are saying.\n\n“Be
 st show we’ve ever seen!” – Gilberte Nowlan – Moncton\, NB\n\n“I
 ’ve seen tributes to ABBA before\, they were great\, but you are the bes
 t. If you come back East we will be there!” –Jack Hayward – Frederic
 ton\, NB\n\n“Just saw your show in Regina. WOW! You guys are amazing –
  I took my (80+) mom and she loved it! The entire group is stunning\, neve
 r seen any performers acknowledge their entire crew\, go into the audience
  and so obviously love what you do! Thank you…we will come again!” –
  Rhonda Lamb – Regina\, SK
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/abra-cadabra-celebrating-the-music-m
 agic-of-abba-april-19-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
