DESCRIPTION:Run With The Squirrels \\(RWTS\\) ….Sunday April 26\, 2026\n
 \nDistances of 5k\, 10k\, 10 mile and half marathon.\n\nLow cost and low f
 rills. No finisher medals\, just the satisfaction that you did something a
 mazing out in mother nature…WooHoo!\n\nThere will be basic aid stations 
 for the 10k\, 10 miler\, and 13.1 mile events.\n\nRace fee does not includ
 e a T shirt. This has been a request by numerous runners to decrease on wa
 ste.\n\nIf you would like to purchase one you have the option to make it a
 n add-on for $15. You must add the shirt before APRIL 10th. There might be
  limited quantities on hand on race day.\n\nCome join us and lets have som
 e trail fun…WooHoo!
URL:https://indyrunners.org/view-race-details/run-with-the-squirrels/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
