BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Finn: A New Musical- At the PB&J Cafe
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260501T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260501T183000
UID:250915n3bBkYXhHEyL2CDKXq0MMg
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage & Screen presents “Finn: A New Musical- 
 At the PB&J Cafe\,” on stage May 1-17 at the Waldron Auditorium. \n\nFr
 om the creator of Doc McStuffins and Vampirina\, Finn is a heartwarming mu
 sical adventure about a young shark on the brink of growing up. As he prep
 ares to join the fearsome Shark Guard\, Finn can’t shake the feeling tha
 t he’s different from the other sharks. Deep inside\, he discovers a col
 orful fish inside him—a part of himself that longs to sparkle\, sing\, a
 nd dance. As Finn embarks on a journey of self-discovery\, friendship\, an
 d adventure\, he finds the courage to be himself! Fun for all ages!\n\n***
 PB&J Cafe***: A Dinner Theater for Kids! At the PB&J Cafe\, young theaterg
 oers will enjoy a meal during the performance and leave with autographs fr
 om their favorite characters. \n\nSee Constellation’s website for more 
 information\, including a detailed performance schedule. Learn more and fi
 nd tickets at https://seeconstellation.org/kids/finn/
LOCATION:Waldron Auditorium
URL:https://seeconstellation.org/kids/finn/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
