UID:260324DoMZcebslkuNorDGc01waw
DESCRIPTION:“May the Schwartz be with you” this May 4th with **Mel Br
 ooks' 1987 cult classic** parody of the *Star Wars* franchise.\n\nIn a d
 istant galaxy\, planet Spaceball has depleted its air supply\, leaving its
  citizens reliant on a product called “Perri-Air.” In desperation\, Sp
 aceball’s leader President Skroob (Mel Brooks) orders the evil Dark Helm
 et (Rick Moranis) to kidnap Princess Vespa (Daphne Zuniga) of oxygen-rich 
 Druidia and hold her hostage in exchange for air.\n\nBut help arrives for 
 the Princess in the form of renegade space pilot Lone Starr (Bill Pullman)
  and his half-man\, half-dog partner\, Barf (John Candy).\n\nRated: PG Len
 gth: 1hr 36mins Format: DCP
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/spaceballs-1987-may-4-2026/
